getSubPartCount

int getSubPartCount()
Get a count of the sub parts within this part. If this is a simple segment, there will be no sub parts. If this is a cable, there will be segments as sub parts.

Returns:
the number of sub parts

getSubPart

INeuronMorphologyPart getSubPart(int i)
Get a sub parts associated with this part at location i. If this is a simple segment, there will be no sub parts. If this is a cable, there will be segments as sub parts.

Parameters:
i -
Returns:
the sub part. null if it is not found.
